  "Notes": [
    {
      "Text": "Security update for mariadb",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for mariadb fixes the following issues:\n\n- CVE-2024-21096: Fixed mysqldump unspecified vulnerability (bsc#1225983).\n- CVE-2023-22084: Fixed a vulnerability allows high privileged attacker with network access via multiple protocols to compromise the server (bsc#1217405).\n\n- Update to 10.6.18.\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
    },
